data.description: Welcome to your Sandy Springs haven! This 2-story end unit condo, just 2 miles from City Springs Center and Perimeter Mall, offers style and convenience. The property boasts hardwood floors, fresh paint throughout, crown molding, and wainscoted walls, this home features two master bedrooms with walk-in closets, a half bath with laundry, and a private patio.  The kitchen is a chef's delight with tiled backsplash, freshly painted cabinets, and stainless steel appliances (refrigerator purchased in 2019 and stove in 2018). With a new AC and furnace in 2018 and the added security of a gated community, this is your ideal home.
